Life Expectancy and Rate of Decline After Lung Volume Reduction Surgery.

Thuppal S(1), Lanzotti N(2), Vost B(2), Crabtree T(2), Markwell S(2), Seadler 
B(2), Rizvi N(1), Sawyer J(2), McCullough K(2), Hazelrigg SR(3).

Author information:
(1)Division of Cardiothoracic Surgery, Department of Surgery, SIU School of 
