Correlation of atherosclerosis and osteoarthritis in ancient Egypt: A 
standardized evaluation of 45 whole-body CT examinations.

Panzer S(1), Augat P(2), Sprenger M(3), Zesch S(4), Rosendahl W(5), Sutherland 
