martin.sprenger@medunigraz.at.
(4)German Mummy Project, Reiss-Engelhorn-Museen Mannheim, Zeughaus C5, D-68159 
Mannheim, Germany. Electronic address: stephanie.zesch@mannheim.de.
(5)German Mummy Project, Reiss-Engelhorn-Museen Mannheim, Zeughaus C5, D-68159 
